data.description: This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a true gem in the heart of Tulare, boasting 1,760 square feet of comfortable living space.  The backyard features a refreshing pool, perfect for cooling off on warm days. Built in 1975, this home has been meticulously maintained and is ready for you to move in and make it your own.
